        p This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.

        h2 Information We Collect
        ul(class='disc py-2')
            li Personal Information: Name, email address, phone number, etc.
            li Usage Data: Information about how you use our website.
            li Cookies: Data stored on your device to enhance user experience.

        h2 How We Use Your Information
        p We may use the information we collect in the following ways:
        ul(class='disc py-2')
            li To provide, operate, and maintain our website.
            li To improve, personalize, and expand our website.
            li To understand and analyze how you use our website.
            li To communicate with you, either directly or through one of our partners.

        h2 Disclosure of Your Information
        p We may share your information in the following situations:
        ul(class='disc py-2')
            li With service providers to monitor and analyze the use of our website.
            li For business transfers, such as mergers or acquisitions.
            li To comply with legal obligations.

        h2 Security of Your Information
        p We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure.

        h2 Your Rights
        p Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal information:
        ul(class='disc py-2')
            li The right to access.
            li The right to rectification.
            li The right to erasure.
            li The right to restrict processing.
            li The right to data portability.

        h2 Changes to This Privacy Policy
        p We may update our privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new privacy policy on this page.

